description: Quartiers Properties AB (publ) is a SE-based company operating in Real Estate Management & Development industry. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2016-07-06. Quartiers Properties AB (publ) is a Sweden-based property developer. The firm develops, sells and manages property on the Sun Coast in Spain. The Company’s operations are divided into property development and property management. The development activity includes the process from acquisition of project and to its completion, which results in management or selling of property. The company also foresees building permits and coordination of the entire development and construction process. The management activity implies administration-related issues. The firm operates through wholly-owned subsidiaries in Spain. The Company’s main shareholders comprise Egonomics AB, Fastighets AB Brannerod and Rocet AB.
